# Forage Cybersecurity Simulations

This repository showcases completed cybersecurity virtual experience programs through [Forage](https://www.theforage.com/). Each simulation reflects real-world scenarios with hands-on tasks in threat analysis, incident response, and security awareness.

## 🧠 Simulations Completed

### 🛡️ Mastercard – Security Awareness
- Identified phishing emails and reported potential threats
- Designed a security awareness training outline
- Developed internal communication strategies for cybersecurity

➡️ [See Details](./Mastercard-Security-Awareness/README.md)

---

### 🧯 AIG – Cybersecurity Incident Response
- Investigated a simulated data breach
- Created an incident report with timeline and recommended actions
- Practiced cross-functional communication and post-incident review

➡️ [See Details](./AIG-Cybersecurity-Incident-Response/README.md)

---

### 📡 Telstra – Cybersecurity Operations
- Triage and analyze incoming SIEM alerts
- Developed basic firewall rules using Python syntax
- Reported suspicious network activity and suggested mitigations

➡️ [See Details](./Telstra-Cybersecurity-Operations/README.md)

---

## 💡 Skills Demonstrated
- Security Awareness & Training
- Incident Response & Digital Forensics
- Threat Intelligence
- SIEM Analysis
- Firewall Rule Development
- Report Writing & Communication
